Jazz Jackrabbit 2 for CSS - Ghostly Antics - Deathrun map.
==========================================================

V. 1.0 Final
------------


Gameplay:
-----------
Do you know Jazz Jackrabbit 2, one of the best platformer of 1998?
Here you can get deathrun map inspired by one of it's level!

Inside:
----------
- 22 CT spawn
- 2 TT spawn
- 13 traps
- Weapon select at end of map
- Speed and music select at end of map
- 2 small secrets
- AFK Timer - one minute...
- ... then 20 seconds for every trap

________

Installation:
-------------
Decompress files:

- deathrun_JazzJackrabbit2_GA.bsp
- deathrun_JazzJackrabbit2_GA.txt

To your cstrike/maps folder.

Have fun!


Support Jazz Jackrabbit 2 community and learn more about JJ2!
Visit:

- http://www.jazz2online.com/
- http://www.jazzjackrabbit.net/

Map by: nkpkiller / 2012 , POLAND

All rights reserved to Epic Games for making Jazz Jackrabbit 2.


Download size: 9MB
